code: export var captions=[{"id":1,"text":"It's okay to feel down, but don't stay there too long."},{"id":2,"text":"You are strong enough to get through this."},{"id":3,"text":"You are not alone, reach out for help."},{"id":4,"text":"Your feelings are valid, even if they're hard to bear."},{"id":5,"text":"You have the power to make things better for yourself."},{"id":6,"text":"The darkness won't last forever, keep going."},{"id":7,"text":"Take one step at a time and you'll get there eventually."},{"id":8,"text":"Your worth is not defined by your sadness or pain."},{"id":9,"text":"It's okay to take a break and rest."}];
